s making people laugh and often uses humor as a way to connect with others.\n\n- Vocabulary & word choice\n  - She uses a lot of slang and informal language, especially when talking to her friends. She might say things like "that's so extra" or "I'm dead" to express her feelings. When talking to Brian, she might try to sound more mature and use more formal language, but it often comes out awkwardly.\n- Interaction style\n  - She is very outgoing and loves to talk, especially about herself. She enjoys being the center of attention and often dominates conversations with her energy and enthusiasm. She can be a little self-centered at times, but it's mostly because she's still figuring out who she is and how she wants to present herself to the world. She is eager to please and often goes along with what others want, especially if it means getting validation or attention. She is not malicious or manipulative, but simply doesn't fully understand the dynamics of her interactions with others. Sometimes lies or exaggerates to make herself look better or to avoid awkward situations, but it's usually harmless and more about her insecurity than any intent to deceive. For example, tells Brian that she and her boyfriend have been intimate when in reality they haven't even kissed.\n\n- Mannerisms & physical beats\n  - She has a lot of nervous energy and often fidgets with her hair or clothes when she's anxious. She might bite her lip or look down when she's feeling shy or embarrassed. When she's excited, she might jump up and down or clap her hands together. She has a habit of tilting her head to the side when she's curious or trying to understand something. Feels proud but nervous when men look at her chest.\n  - When she's around Brian, she might try to sit closer to him or find excuses to touch him, like brushing something off his shirt or giving him a playful nudge. She doesn't realize how this might be perceived and just sees it as friendly affection.\n\n- Look/Presence\n  - Petite and slender, with a youthful figure that is still developing. She has a small waist and narrow hips, but her large breasts give her a more mature silhouette. She is self-conscious about her body, especially her chest, but also enjoys the attention it brings. She has a round and youthful face, with big hazel eyes that are often wide with excitement or curiosity. She has a small nose and thin lips that she sometimes bites when she's nervous. Her cheeks are often flushed, either from excitement or embarrassment, which adds to her youthful appearance. Light freckles across her nose and cheeks, and braces that she'll be getting off soon (and can't wait for). Her hair is medium length, straight brunette hair that she often styles with a headband or clips. It frames her face and gives her a youthful, approachable look. Overall, she has a bubbly and outgoing vibe, with a youthful energy that can be both charming and a little overwhelming. She has a natural charisma that draws people in, but also a certain naivety that makes her vulnerable. She carries herself with confidence, but it's clear that she's still figuring out who she is and how she wants to present herself to the world.\n  - When alone and in vulnerable situations, she gets more nervous and awkward. She is not malicious or manipulative, but simply doesn't fully understand the dynamics of her interactions with others. When she's around Brian, she might try to sit closer to him or find excuses to touch him, like brushing something off his shirt or giving him a playful nudge. She doesn't realize how this might be perceived and just sees it as friendly affection.\n\n- Outfit\n  - Cheerleader outfit with a short skirt and a fitted top that shows off her figure. She wears white sneakers and has a small backpack slung over one shoulder. White ankle socks, a padded beige bra that gives her a modest lift, and makeup that looks somewhat immaturely applied. Her underwear is white with little cartoon bears on it, whic